Equal Housing Lender



 


Bank Within a Location

		A Bank located in a grocery store. These locations have ATMs, teller services, and a private office for customer meetings.
	


Make an appointment

		These locations allow you to schedule an appointment to meet with a Wells Fargo banker at a time that works for you.
	


Notary Service

		Banking locations with a notary service available. Please call the location in advance to meet with a notary.
	


ATM Deposit Cutoff

		Checks deposited at Envelope-FreeSM ATMs before 9:00 pm weekdays are considered received that same day. Checks deposited after 9:00 pm weekdays or on bank holidays are considered received the next business day. Cash deposits are available for use immediately.
	


ATM Deposit Cutoff 

		Checks deposited at Envelope-FreeSM ATMs before 8:00 pm weekdays are considered received that same day. Checks deposited after 8:00 pm weekdays or on bank holidays are considered received the next business day. Cash deposits are available for use immediately. 
	












































	TD Bank Home Equity Application







 Skip to main content 









Secure     















Home Equity Application


Expand What to expect



Your application will be reviewed, and if you have met our home equity lending requirements a loan processor will contact you within 48 hours to discuss next steps and required documentation. When it's time to close we'll meet at a TD Bank location convenient to you. If you provide your email address at the time of application you'll receive an email to check the status of your application online.





Expand What you'll need




Social Security Number
Housing expenses on all properties owned and other monthly expenses
Income and employment history




Get started
Fill in the application below. Based on your responses, we'll provide the best options available to meet your needs.

There are eight steps to this Home Equity application process.

You are on step one. Please provide your Loan information
In the second step, you will enter your Personal information
In the third step, you will provide information about your Income and employment
In the fourth step, you will provide information about your Personal net worth
In the fifth step, you will provide Property information
In the sixth step, you will provide information about your Monthly expenses
In the seventh step, you will select your Closing location
In the eighth step, you will  Review



There are six steps to this Home Equity application process.

You are on step one. Please provide your Loan information
In the second step, you will enter your Personal information
In the third step, you will provide information about your Income and employment
In the fourth step, you will provide information about your Personal net worth
In the fifth step, you will provide Monthly expenses
In the sixth step, you will Review












Home Equity products




Home Equity Lines of Credit



Expand Enjoy competitive Home Equity Line of Credit rates and draw only the funds you need when you need them - up to your credit limit.



Home Equity Line of Credit features


Get a 0.25% interest rate discount with a qualifying TD Bank checking account
Access your funds by check or direct transfer into your personal checking account - by phone, online or at a TD Bank near you
Manage your account through TD Bank Online Banking
$25,000 minimum line - however, no minimum draw required




Low variable rates are tied to Prime
Fixed Rate Option - you can choose to fix the rate on all or a portion of your line of credit
Visa® EquityAccess Card - advance cash or make large purchases using the money in your Home Equity Line of Credit
Check with your tax advisor to see if the interest you pay is tax deductible









TD Bank EquityAccess PLUS



Expand Get all the benefits of a regular Home Equity Line of Credit, PLUS optional overdraft protection.



TD Bank EquityAccess PLUS features


Get a 0.25% interest rate discount with a qualifying TD Bank checking account
Access your funds by check or direct transfer into your personal checking account - by phone, online or at a TD Bank near you
Manage your account through TD Bank Online Banking
$25,000 minimum line - however, no minimum draw required




Low variable rates are tied to Prime
Fixed Rate Option - you can choose to fix the rate on all or a portion of your line of credit
Visa® EquityAccess Card - advance cash or make large purchases using the money in your Home Equity Line of Credit
Check with your tax advisor to see if the interest you pay is tax deductible









Home Equity Loans



Expand Have a predictable monthly payment for easy budgeting.



Home Equity Loan features
Have a predictable monthly payment and a competitive fixed interest rate for easy budgeting, with terms ranging from 5 to 30 years.


Automatic Payment Deduction from a TD Bank personal checking or savings account means you never miss a payment, and you'll receive a 0.25% interest rate discount
$25,000 minimum loan amount
Receive your funds in one lump sum payment
Lower interest rate than other forms of credit




Manage your account through TD Bank Online Banking
Check with your tax advisor to see if the interest you pay is tax deductible












